  Hyper-Jumps    :  Hyper-Jump Modules can be found in many places in the
             Dungeons or can be bought from the supply store.  When using
             a Hyper-jump module, the user will be prompted for a direction.
             simply press the arrow key or number key that represents the
             direction that you wish to jump and you will jump to the
             adjacent room in that direction.
                Hyper-Jump Modules Looks Like this ---> 


  Teleports      :  Teleports can only be bought from the supply store.
             When using teleports, the user is prompted to enter the
             room number to which he/she desires to teleport to.  Valid
             room numbers are in the range of 0 to 99.

  OverView Maps  :  If a player finds an Overview Map, he/she will be
             allowed to view the entire level of rooms and be able to see
             how the rooms are connected.  Maps can be found or bought
             at the supply store.  If you Kill another player and he/she
             has a Map you will become the new owner of the map and then
             will be able to view it.  Once You advance levels, you will
             need to find or buy another map for the new level.
