  Magnetic Floor Panels :  You may walk over the magnetic floor panels
             at any time, however, the shots you fire and the shots that
             are fired at you may be deflected or absorbed by the magnetic
             floor panels.
                Magnetic Floor Panels look like this ---> ฐ

  Leaving Items  : Once you find a safe place, you might want to store some
             of the items that you carry.

  Advancing Levels : When you find the Exit Room, there will be an area
             Labeled "EXIT".  If you have the SEVEN XENO Jewels in your
             posession, You will be allowed to cross the Jewel Barrier into
             the Exit Portal..




